overview: The End is a skateboarding video by Birdhouse Skateboards. Some of the skaters incorporated a short story into their video parts. These stories include Rick McCrank looking for a job, Steve Berra being killed by an unknown attacker, Andrew Reynolds hanging out with a monkey, Heath Kirchart and Jeremy Klein's rampaging mayhem in the city and Bucky Lasek taking down Tony Hawk so that he can become the number one skateboarder.
title: The End
